name: TenX
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en:
What is the project about?
First AMM exchange to launch on TENET network with built in liquidity farming 

What makes your project unique?
the fact that this is the first AMM to be launched on the network, that is backed by the TENET Foundation and has liquidity farming

History of your project.
Launched 29/6/23- with LP supplied by the TENET foundation. Community is growing strong over both twitter and telegram. current MCAP around $650k. Listing on GeckoTerminal is already live. 

What’s next for your project?
To continue to be the number 1 AMM on the Tenet network (current competitor Tendies has significantly less MCAP and users)
We look to bring more farming/pools to the project and partner with more projects to build on the impressive start we have made and increase our audience and token price. We will continue to work in conjunction with the tenet foundation. 

What can your token be used for?
swapping, pooling, adding LP of selected tokens on the tenet network.

We look to bring more farming/pools to the project and partner with more projects to build on the impressive start we have made and increase our audience and token price. We will continue to work in conjunction with the tenet foundation. 

What can your token be used for?
swapping, pooling, adding LP of selected tokens on the tenet network.
description.sl:
What is the project about?
First AMM exchange to launch on TENET network with built in liquidity farming 

What makes your project unique?
the fact that this is the first AMM to be launched on the network, that is backed by the TENET Foundation and has liquidity farming

History of your project.
Launched 29/6/23- with LP supplied by the TENET foundation. Community is growing strong over both twitter and telegram. current MCAP around $650k. Listing on GeckoTerminal is already live. 

What’s next for your project?
To continue to be the number 1 AMM on the Tenet network (current competitor Tendies has significantly less MCAP and users)
We look to bring more farming/pools to the project and partner with more projects to build on the impressive start we have made and increase our audience and token price. We will continue to work in conjunction with the tenet foundation. 

What can your token be used for?
swapping, pooling, adding LP of selected tokens on the tenet network.
